source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_SEQ_00<tab>Godafre appears in need of some tight-lipped assistance.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_SEQ_00<tab>ラジアタのゴダフレは、取ってきてほしいものがあるそうだ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the unheavy package to Godafre.

TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_000<tab>Godsdammit...
This'll all fall through without the goods, but how am I supposed to get there and back without─
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_000<tab>ちくしょー……。
これじゃ、せっかくの商材もパーじゃねぇか。
どうにかして、取りにいかねぇと……。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_001<tab>Bloody hells, where did you spring from!? Bah, never mind that─can you keep your mouth shut, <var 08 E905 ((lass)) ((lad)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_001<tab>……お、アンタ。
口が堅そうな顔してんな。
ちょっと耳を貸してくれや。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_002<tab>I've a package hidden away over in Specula Imperatoris, and I need someone discreet to go and fetch it for me.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_002<tab>スペキュラ・インペラトリスの一角に、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DAE01 /var>」を隠してある。
それを、こそーっと取ってきてくれねぇか？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_003<tab>Don't let its size dissuade you─the thing's as light as air. I'd head over there myself, you know, but if folk were to spot me it would cause <var 1A 02 /var>complications<var 1A 01 /var> for future dealings. Well, go on! There's a reward in it for you!
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_003<tab>大事な商材だから、俺が取りに行きたいのはやまやまだが、
変に目をつけられると、商売に差し支えるからな……。
分け前を弾むから、頼んだぜ？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_004<tab>The package is in a secluded corner of Specula Imperatoris. Try to slip in and out with no one the wiser if you can manage it, eh?
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_004<tab>スペキュラ・インペラトリスの一角に、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DAE01 /var>」を隠してある。
それを、こそーっと取ってきてくれねぇか？
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_010<tab>どうだい、見つからずに例のブツを持ち帰れたか？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_020<tab>Aye, that's the stuff! You've done this sort of thing before, eh?
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_020<tab>この包み、間違いねぇ！
よく取ってきてくれたな、ありがとよ！！

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_021<tab>I see what you're thinking: “What's in this big package that weighs next to naught?” Well, I'd better satisfy your curiosity before you start asking questions to the wrong people. It's tobacco, my friend─made right here in Radiata.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_021<tab>変に軽かったから、中身が気になるって？
仕方ねえ、取ってきてくれた礼に教えてやるよ。
これは、ラジアタ産の煙草だ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_022<tab>I used to be a porter for the imperials, you see, carting supplies around all day until my back was screaming. The officers would complain about their military-issue pipeweed, so I started earning myself a few small luxuries by smuggling in Radiata's best. On the quiet, of course.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_022<tab>俺は、あの施設で荷運びとしてこき使われててな。
そのとき奴らが、支給品の煙草がマズイとケチつけててよ。
それで、この煙草を横流しして、小遣い稼ぎしてたんだ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_023<tab>And I'd appreciate it if you could keep quiet, too. I mean to sell to the Resistance forces next, and they'd best not know about my previous customers.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_023<tab>おっと、この話は秘密だぜ？
なんせ、次のお客は解放軍だからな。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_025<tab>Here's the reward I promised you. Half for the job, and half to keep your lips sealed, understand?
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ822_02850_GODAFRE_000_025<tab>ほら、これが約束の分け前だ。
口止め料も兼ねているから、よろしくな？
